data.description: Come experience this picturesque property that captures the essence of country living while offering exciting opportunities for expansion. Situated on a generous 3.58-acre lot, this unique estate boasts an charming farmhouse, a historic barn, and an abundance of character, making it a truly special find. Not to mention the new roof and beautiful hardwoods. 3BR/2BA with the primary bedroom on the main level. Spacious and wired, multi room storage bldg. With 3.58 acres, there is the exciting possibility of subdividing the land to create two additional homesites, making this an ideal investment opportunity. Experience the tranquility of Lexington while still being conveniently located near schools, shopping, dining, and major commuter routes. Second floor ceilings are 6ft-not included in square footage-507 extra square feet. Selling as-is.
